<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ạ̉nt ʿẓym ạlbrkạt</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạản̊ta ʿaẓīmu ạl̊barakāt̊
 yā rabũ lil̊ʿabīd̊
 rusẖ̊duⁿ waʿaẘnuⁿ watẖabāt̊
 wamal̊jāuⁿ̉ waṭīd̊

[V2]
 yamīnuka taqūdunā
 ại̹lay̱ maday̱ ạldãh̊ri
 wataʿ̊tanī biḥif̊ẓinā
 fī ạl̊barĩ wāl̊baḥ̊ri

[V3]
 ại̹dẖā ṭamā ạl̊maẘju ạlrãfīʿ̊
 wahājati ạl̊mīāh̊
 naʿ̊lamu ạảnãka ạlsãmīʿ̊
 waṣāḥibu ạlnãjāh̊

[V4]
 tah̊dā biạảm̊rika ạlrĩyāḥ̊
 ṭaẘʿaⁿạ limā turīd̊
 fanan̊ẓuru ạl̊baḥ̊ra ạs̊tarāḥ̊
 min̊ kadĩhi ạlsẖãdīd̊</lyrics>
<aka>ạnt ʿẓym ạlbrkạt</aka>
</song>